description: Were these lottery winners cursed? From 2018, Rhoda Toth and her husband blew an entire $13 million Florida lottery jackpot, and she ended up in prison for tax fraud. In 2025, Edwin Castro, the winner of the biggest lottery jackpot in history, lost his home in the Los Angeles wildfires. In 2019, Eileen Murray's ex-husband won $273 million in the lottery just a few months after they got divorced. Inside Edition Digital's Andrea Swindall has more.
title: Were These Lottery Winners Cursed?
